name: Lufthansa A340-313 [D-AIFA] Close Up Taxi and Takeoff from Montreal-Trudeau ᴴᴰ
description:
Always great to see an A340! Here we have Lufthansa's daily flight from Montreal to Frankfurt taxiing up close and departing runway 24L, back in July. Enjoy this very clean looking A340!

Thanks for watching!

Airline: Lufthansa (DLH/LH) (operated by Lufthansa CityLine)
Aircraft: Airbus A340-300 (A343)

Engines: 4x CFMI CFM56-5C4 
Registration: D-AIFA
Route: Montreal-Trudeau (YUL) - Frankfurt-Main (FRA)
Callsign: Lufthansa 479 heavy

Date filmed: July 18, 2017
Local time: 1700
